{"tid":1391984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［打機砌裝］英雄級防具原料。發現！","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:44:22.000Z","uid":243011,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c0bed41fc41d74d0e25aff121a05407e3a45cf","tid":1391984,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"岩岩訓晏覺就發夢啦，係夢入面得知，其實香港d路牌，可以圓可以方，亦都有分厚度。<br />\n<br />\n原來香港係有廠幫客人度身訂造路牌，我個親戚報夢比我知，原來一塊普通路牌大約係40蚊左右，因為佢地以噸計，所以好難去估算每塊大概幾錢。<br />\n<br />\n拿，整路牌好啦，唔好搵五金焊一焊把手，或者鑽兩個窿用黎固定係上身某個地方<br />\n<br />\n跟住個夢醒左，唔記得邊道有得買/有得訂，但夢入面個親戚話我知，香港一定有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KcNtBt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KcNtBt.png&h=405261a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OMdtc3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOMdtc3c.png&h=d3089c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiddo9W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjiddo9W.png&h=c96b58a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExkrJ90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExkrJ90.png&h=7c871b1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffb59fd3a7f15d54f04da3b47cd8d91aa753a17b","tid":1391984,"uid":243011,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"我係咪開錯左時事台？仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424dc67f3ddeb5205812c9bc85bddeadd7b3d76f","tid":1391984,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"推到有人應為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42718b001a6af94521c962e4772b