 />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3544d3f4e8689259b357874d0f656a6c97fb72","tid":1391984,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"推到人前線應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcce092e2b1374fe26f55521d07d61f0d4fa09e","tid":1391984,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"推到有前線應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a36f5c8700a7bf5c4ae924bc7a93e66f08f5c7","tid":1391984,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"有用資訊"},{"pid":"b906b6d843bcd0775984462e3c0652229098631c","tid":1391984,"uid":218,"like":1,"dis